OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FIt will be a dry day with some
OL,6,Fbright or sunny spells. Feeling quite
OL,7,Fwarm in the west but cooler across
OL,8,FDown and Antrim with southeasterly
OL,9,Fbreeze.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FA bright end to the day then
OL,12,Fa dry night with long clear spells.
OL,13,FBecoming chilly overnight in some
OL,14,Fsheltered valleys.
OL,15,
OL,16,CFriday:FAnother dry day with long
OL,17,Fperiods of sunshine. Becoming rather
OL,18,Fwarm inland by the afternoon but
OL,19,Fcooler near the east coast.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
